      Simplicity	  Direct servlet execution
  Interceptor Overhead
      Bean resolution
      Handler mapping
      Reflection call
   Conclusion:
      👉 Filter = lightweight
      👉 Interceptor = feature-rich
 Why Interceptor Cannot Replace Filter?
      Feature	                      Filter	Interceptor
      Runs before DispatcherServlet	✅	    ❌
      Modify request/response       raw	✅	Limited
      Works without Spring	        ✅	    ❌
      🚨 Example👉 CORS, Encoding: Must happen before Spring. So interceptor ❌ cannot replace

